  <brief_title>Conventional Versus Modified Laparoscopic Cholecystectomy</brief_title>
  <official_title>Randomized Controlled Trial Comparing Between The Conventional Technique of Laparoscopic Cholecystectomy and A Proposed Modified Technique</official_title>
  <sponsors>
